text: Eliana Ramos (23 December 1988 â€“ 13 February 2007) was a Uruguayan fashion model who was signed with Dotto Models. On 13 February 2007, Ramos died from a heart attack brought on by anorexia. Her sister Luisel, who was also a model, died from the same cause of death six months before.
